outputs.output_descr:
The Family and Battered Women Protection Programme (FBWPP) was launched by Dr.Aisha Gaddafi the Secretary of Watassemo Charity Society on 06/03/2009.
A hotline under the number 1515 for receiving complaints of domestic violence was created.  With a contribution of €25000 towards the project the Netherlands Embassy in Tripoli hopes support the FBWP  programme in general and to develop the capacities of the staff in order to them to perform their duties effectively
